Flight Simulator Advanced
/ Privacy Policy
Welcome to FS Advanced! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information that is collected by FS Advanced and how it is used.
Information We Collect
FS Advanced does not collect any personal data or information that can be used to identify you as an individual.
Use of IDFA (Identifier for Advertisers)
We use the Identifier for Advertisers (IDFA) solely for the purpose of serving targeted advertisements within the game. The IDFA is a unique identifier for mobile devices and is used by mobile operating systems to allow advertisers to provide you with more relevant advertising experiences.
How We Use Your Information
The IDFA is used to enhance your advertising experience by delivering ads that are more relevant to your interests. We do not store, collect, or link the IDFA to any personal identity information, nor do we share the IDFA with third parties.
Data Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access to or unauthorized alteration, disclosure, or destruction of data. We do not collect personal information, and we ensure the confidentiality of any data collected.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to
contact us
